# Common Package (`common/`)

The `[common/](mdc:common/common/common)` directory contains shared code used across the monorepo.

-   It is written in TypeScript.
-   It uses Rollup for bundling (see `[rollup.config.mjs](mdc:common/common/common/rollup.config.mjs)`).
-   TypeScript configuration can be found in `[tsconfig.json](mdc:common/common/common/tsconfig.json)`.
-   Dependencies are managed in `[package.json](mdc:common/common/common/package.json)`.
-   This package is installed as a dependency in the `frontend` and `backend` packages.
